3)Working of spring boot?
1)Spring boot starts by scanning the starter dependencies in pom.xml
download and auto-configuration the module as watever we  included in pom.xml

dwonlaod  haar baar nhi hoga jb maven reload or build kre ge tbhi download hoga.
Ex: We have to create a web application then we have to put spring-boot-starter-web dependency in pom.xml 
when we start the project springboot download all the dependency require for web
and configure  the things like spring mvc.









